<html lang='ko' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge' />
    <style type='text/css'>
      /* 이메일 클라이언트 호환성 */
      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto,
          'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      table {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        border-spacing: 0;
        width: 100%;
      }
      td {
        border-collapse: collapse;
        vertical-align: top;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1a73e8;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      }
      .logo-subtitle {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        margin-top: 5px;
        font-weight: normal;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer-link {
        color: #1a73e8;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 8px;
      }
      .footer-link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .divider {
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          width: 100% !important;
          max-width: 100% !important;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 30px 15px;
        }
        .header {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }
        .footer {
          padding: 20px 15px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;"
  >
    <table
      border='0'
      cellpadding='0'
      cellspacing='0'
      style='width: 100%; background-color: #f5f5f5;'
    >
      <tr>
        <td align='center' style='padding: 0;'>
          <!-- 📧 Main Container -->
          <table
            border='0'
            cellpadding='0'
            cellspacing='0'
            style='max-width: 600px; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; margin: 20px auto;'
          >
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background-color: #f9f9f9;'
              >
                <div
                  style='font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a73e8; letter-spacing: -0.5px;'
                >bluecollar.cv</div>
                <div
                  style='font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 5px; font-weight: normal;'
                >전문가와 만나는 가장 쉬운 방법</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Content -->
            <tr>
              <td style='padding: 40px 30px;'>
                {{{body}}}
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td
                style='background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 30px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; font-size: 12px; color: #666;'
              >
                <div style='text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px;'>
                  <a
                    href='https://bluecollar.cv'
                    style='color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px;'
                  >서비스 주소</a>
                  <span style='color: #d0d0d0;'>|</span>
                  <a
                    href='https://bluecollar.cv/privacy'
                    style='color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px;'
                  >개인정보 처리방침</a>
                  <span style='color: #d0d0d0;'>|</span>
                  <a
                    href='https://bluecollar.cv/terms'
                    style='color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 8px;'
                  >이용약관</a>
                </div>
                <div
                  style='text-align: center; color: #999; margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding-top: 15px;'
                >
                  <p style='margin: 5px 0; font-size: 11px; color: #666;'>이
                    메일에 답장하시면 support@bluecollar.cv로 전달되며, 빠르게
                    답변드리겠습니다.</p>
                  <p style='margin: 8px 0;'>이메일 수신을 원하지 않으시면
                    <a
                      href='https://bluecollar.cv/unsubscribe'
                      style='color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none;'
                    >여기</a>를 클릭해주세요.</p>
                  <p style='margin: 5px 0; color: #999;'>© 2026 BlueCollar. All
                    rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>